LIsp-Flavoured Tensor

further development after the tutorial

to generate OpenCL code for conv.model

  # generate conv.c and conv.yaml (schedule)
  python -m lift conv func conv.model

  # generate conv_host.c and conv_kernel.cl
  ppcg -v --no-reschedule --load-schedule=conv.yaml --target=opencl conv.c

Requirements:

* Python 2.7
* ply (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ply)
* islpy (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/islpy)
* ppcg (http://ppcg.gforge.inria.fr/)
